window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Four years after the Nihil and the Order has a new threat.</p> <p>A clay tablet is discovered at an excavation in Knossos, Crete. The text is written in a language that no one can decipher, but the Nazis have come to claim it and Napoleon sends his own Savants Temporal to the Minoan tomb.</p> <p>Meanwhile, something ancient is infecting the descendants of the great houses of Europe.</p> <p>Book four in the best selling Infinity Engine series.</p>"; 
